   "source": "<ROUTINE POWER-TRANSMITTER-F (\"AUX\" (NUM 0))\n\t <SET NUM <CANAL-LOC>>\n\t <COND (<OR <G? .NUM 31>\n\t\t    <L? .NUM 13>>\n\t\t<CANT-SEE ,POWER-TRANSMITTER>)\n\t       (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t\t<DESCRIBE-POWER-TRANSMITTER .NUM>\n\t\t<CRLF>)\n\t       (<TOUCHING? ,POWER-TRANSMITTER>\n\t\t<CANT-REACH ,POWER-TRANSMITTER>)>>"
