   "endLine": 3598,
   "source": "<ROUTINE HARMLESS-SNAP (STRING)\n\t <TELL\n\"   The calm water is suddenly shattered by the jaws of a huge Martian \"\n.STRING \" snapping harmlessly toward you. Good thing you were in the\nraft.\" CR>>"
