   "file": "mars.zil",
   "line": 3951,
   "endLine": 3962,
   "source": "<ROUTINE I-CRY ()\n\t <COND (<IN? ,BLANKET ,BABY>\n\t\t<DEQUEUE I-CRY>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<NOT <VISIBLE? ,BABY>>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"   The baby continues to wail at the top of its lungs.\">\n\t\t<COND (<PROB 12>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\" It's amazing that such small lungs have such a high top.\">)>\n\t\t<CRLF>)>>"
